OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBrazil gripped by          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'unbearable' heatwave      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Red alerts have been issued for almost 
OL,6, 3,000 towns and cities across Brazil,  
OL,7, which have been experiencing an        
OL,8, unprecedented heatwave.                
OL,10,FRio de Janeiro recorded 42.5C on Sunday
OL,11,F- a record for November - and high     
OL,12,Fhumidity on Tuesday meant that it felt 
OL,13,Flike 58.5C, municipal authorities said.
OL,15,FMore than a hundred million people have
OL,16,Fbeen affected by the heat, which is    
OL,17,Fexpected to last until at least Friday.
OL,19,FOfficials have attributed it to the El 
OL,20,FNino phenomenon and climate change.    
